    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（降りる駅が近づいているんだが、気付いてなさそうだ）\n（そろそろ声を掛けておくか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "渚、そろそろ降りる支度を始めてくれ\n……おーい、渚？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2700.0000000000027,
          "startTime": 47.5
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5300.000000000005,
          "startTime": 50.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、ここの繋がりで、ここの動きも……\nあっ、すみません、もう少し待って下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4200.000000000003,
          "startTime": 57.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.006869666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "……よし、メモ終わりっと。お待たせしました！\n行きましょう、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.7243299804
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "って、あれっ！？　扉が閉まって……\nで、電車、出ちゃいましたよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.1459174158
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "降りるのは次の駅だから大丈夫だよ\n集中していたから、少し早めに声を掛けておいたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.0086160662
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "良かったぁ。さすがです、{user}さん\nせっかく新曲でセンターを任せてもらえたのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "お仕事に遅刻なんてしたら、月ストのみんなに\n合わせる顔がなくなっちゃうところでしたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.4126969022
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "それに、学校から現場に向かうと、いつも到着が\nギリギリなんですけど、今日は早めに着きそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "あ、でもその分、迷惑掛けちゃったりしてませんか？\n私が一杯一杯な分、フォローしてもらっちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.4868238452
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "今は渚の勝負時だからな。全然迷惑じゃないよ\nそういえば、すずがセンターの時もいろいろあったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.4007240299
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "え、すずちゃんが？\nえっと……良かったら、聞かせてくれますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.365704346
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "初めてのセンターで、すずも一杯一杯だったんだろう\n仕事の移動中は、いつも考え込んでいる様子だったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.9666585286,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、大好きなポテトチップスは食べたかったのか\nコンビニに寄るたびに毎回、無意識に買っていたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.4333251953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.0817357067
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "凄い時なんて、一日で十袋も買って、後になって\n「こんなに食べきれませんわー！？」って慌ててたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.8333251953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、そうだったんですね\nそういえば前にお裾分けしてもらったことがありました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.0666585286,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.2292172436
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "そっか、一杯一杯なのは私だけじゃないんだ。でも\nこんなこと話したら、すずちゃんに怒られちゃうかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.4968236536,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "確かに……それもそうだな\nじゃあ、ここだけの秘密で頼むよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.2666493733,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 177.4419162594
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（本当はすずから頼まれたんだけどな。もし渚が悩んで）\n（いたら、自分の成功談や失敗談を伝えてほしいって）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.2666585285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
